{"tid":729777,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"建議設立「精華台」","createTime":"2018-07-05T00:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T05:09:54.000Z","uid":104443,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"648b4465a6d335505cdf007a378d57c74ebd767a","tid":729777,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"最近「高學歷廢青」巴打喺時事台連出多個高質文，我自己覺得受益匪淺，難得children可以有巴打提出咁精闢嘅見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但高質post總會有1001嘅一日，為咗想比更多未來嘅巴打睇返以往嘅好post，故本人心生此念，建議連登可以仿效其他討論區設立「精華台」，希望連登各位admin憐聽我嘅願望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">設立「精華台」好處：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.）保存高質post</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有鑑連登喺每一個post都設定咗1001留言限制，一旦達到限制就冇得再留言，好自然地呢個高質post就會沉，以後嘅人唔特登search都唔會見到，設立「精華台」之後，可以有效保存呢類高質post，集中起嚟，令有興趣嘅讀者或者想學下嘢嘅人可以過嚟呢度，好輕易可以睇番。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.）照顧未來嘅讀者</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭先講過，當一個post沉咗之後，以後嘅人唔特登search都唔會見到，而且之後嘅人亦都未必知道之前原來有呢啲高質post，咁樣會令到未來嘅讀者冇機會接觸到之前嘅高質post，設立「精華台」之後，可以令部分因事而錯過咗1001討論「時間」而又唔知情嘅巴絲睇返之前嘅post，增廣見聞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">設計細節</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.）於「精華台」仍舊作各台嘅分部處理</span><br />\n<br />\n亦即係「精華台」入面仍然要分類每一個原本屬於唔同台嘅post，而唔係乜春都混埋一齊，咁樣會方便讀者搜索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入選標準</span></span><br />\n以下係我對入選標準嘅小小提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.）內文可見學識淵博<br />\n<br />\n2.）post主有獨特見解，而又有益於大眾<br />\n<br />\n3.）留言可見譽聲洪洪，各人對post主讚不絕口，正評連連者<br />\n<br />\n4.）以學術，勸導，處世，邏輯澄明等等正面意義為主<br />\n<br />\n5.）嚴禁色情淫蕩主題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本人心繋連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家可以接受我嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果大家諗到啲嘢亦希望大家可以補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再一次希望連登各位admin憐聽我嘅願望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db5bcc962ee208e9cd276a0ed4df9b42e1bcfe7","tid":729777,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f55eca515f966008aa541d3c0c43c1f28d18c274","tid":729777,"uid":72943,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"開個低質台放曬d小學雞入去會唔會好d"},{"pid":"96afb13e0f8aa4458f3a8d4c73b5d8a7323c26e1","tid":729777,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5db5bcc962ee208e9cd276a0ed4df9b42e1bcfe7","tid":729777,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"你啲五毛大中華膠post搬去黑洞就差唔多"},{"pid":"09d1f3e0c30e48c45d062ef406bef95700dad6d5","tid":729777,"uid":101976,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"咁谷德超勁啲Post一定唔撚洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都係精華"},{"pid":"2b577d4f46adcf5da86003a6cdad673c926f7368","tid":729777,"uid":104443,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09d1f3e0c30e48c45d062ef406bef95700dad6d5","tid":729777,"uid":101976,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"咁谷德超勁啲Post一定唔撚洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都係精華"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:38:11.000Z","msg":"4.）以學術，勸導，處世，邏輯澄明等等正面意義為主<br />\n<br />\n5.）嚴禁色情淫蕩主題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cl